{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completionHandler:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^)()) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view. If "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The block executed after the animation finishes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"